doctrine of contributory infringement

00:19:52.510 --> 00:19:56.880
could be established by showing that
the defendant quote provided the site

00:19:56.880 --> 00:20:03.890
and facilities for known
infringing activity close quote.

00:20:03.890 --> 00:20:07.470
With respect to vicarious
infringement, the Ninth Circuit

00:20:07.470 --> 00:20:11.680
ruled that Cherry Auction
controlled the flea market site

00:20:11.680 --> 00:20:15.080
and had unconstrained
authority to expel any vendor.

00:20:15.080 --> 00:20:16.950
It, thus, plainly had
the right and ability

00:20:16.950 --> 00:20:20.110
to supervise the infringing activity.

00:20:20.110 --> 00:20:22.670
More importantly and
controversially, the court

00:20:22.670 --> 00:20:26.130
