defendant to earn more money.

00:20:50.550 --> 00:20:53.860
It should be apparent that this
is an expansive interpretation.

00:20:53.860 --> 00:20:58.040
Taken literally, it would
encompass many kinds of behavior

00:20:58.040 --> 00:21:00.640
in which the financial
benefit to the defendant

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:06.701
